FBIS4-14743 "drsov064_f_94029" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk Representative Appointed to Sevastopol Kravchuk Representative Appointed to Sevastopol LD0204182194 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 1500 GMT 2 Apr 94 LD0204182194 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Ukrainian BFN [Text] In a decree, the Ukrainian president has appointed Mykola Mykhaylovych Hlushko representative of the Ukrainian president in the town of Sevastopol and has released him from the post of first deputy chairman of Sevastopol town state administration.
